  "texts": [
    "We reiterate that we used 10 meters and ∼3 meters (10 ft) as the thresholds for computing well location and depth offset, respectively.",
    "For the 150 Colorado drilling well record documents, the information extraction results obtained by Llama 2 70B with four different prompts are presented in Table 2.",
    "Clearly, excellent location extraction performances were obtained using Llama 2 70B model for Colorado cases.",
    "As shown in this table, the values of AOS for location reach 100% despite the varying contents of the prompt.",
    "This observation reveals that the locations of all 150 wells were correctly extracted from the well drilling completion reports in Colorado using the LLM and proposed prompts."
  ]
}